	"system": {
		"description": "<p>You are a rogue’s rogue, skilled in stealth, trickery, and larceny. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li><p>Your Dexterity, Intelligence, or Charisma score increases by +1, to a maximum of 20.</p></li><li><p>You gain proficiency with the Deception, Sleight of Hand, or Stealth skill. If you are already proficient with all three, you gain an expertise die to one of your choice. Your maximum expertise die size for all three of these skills is a d10.</p></li><li><p>You gain an additional @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.o2eh10mg3xh9tbu3]{skill trick}. It does not count against your skill tricks known.</p></li><li><p>You gain proficiency with a single rare weapon with the Stealthy property.</p></li><li><p>Your Footpad follower becomes Seasoned.</p></li></ul>",
